00:10:09.470 --> 00:10:16.660 position:56%
And I was thinking about the absence
of that noise, and also how kind

00:10:16.660 --> 00:10:18.960
of the expectation that
there was always going

00:10:18.960 --> 00:10:24.200
to be another name added
to the list of those --

00:10:24.200 --> 00:10:28.090
