indicate by stopping.

00:10:35.120 --> 00:10:37.930
"Sunrise Foley Square."

00:10:37.930 --> 00:10:42.310
"One siren stained the
morning in concentric rings.

00:10:42.310 --> 00:10:44.010
Another starts up.

00:10:44.010 --> 00:10:45.860
