00:10:57.670 --> 00:10:58.970
Thickening.

00:10:58.970 --> 00:11:01.260
Flowing over and around.

00:11:01.260 --> 00:11:07.690
A lack that could be displaced,
but not entirely dispersed.

00:11:07.690 --> 00:11:10.480
An air bubble trapped
in rubber tubing.

00:11:10.480 --> 00:11:14.040
